title: HOUR 2- Jane Slater and Jessica Mendoza Oct 21, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 2- Jane Slater and Jessica Mendoza Oct 21, 2020
description:
Jane Slater talks to Dan about the injuries on the Cowboys but says it is frustrating to see lack of effort on the defensive side of the ball. Jane says if you look at the film, you can see that the team is not buying in to the Mike McCarthy system. Jessica Mendoza talks to Dan about being female and being on the World Series Baseball broadcast team.
